</div>

<div class="dashboard-modules table index_table index">
  <div class="dashboard-module">
    <div class="module-body factoid-parent">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 6px;">üöß <strong>WIP!</strong> This section will eventually give a full indication of how we're tracking as per the Bottom-Up Leadership Experiment; but for now, some of these metrics are still being incorporated into Stacks.</p>
      <a href="https://www.notion.so/garden3d/Introducing-Bottom-Up-Leadership-at-garden3d-93cfbd78330245d1a14cb1ad312b0290" target="_blank">
